      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis power-law exponent) is scoped out at MRL 2. A single validated model form (SST k-omega with Giersiepen hemolysis model) is used consistently; comparative model-form sensitivity is not required at this risk level."
