      "factorStatus": "not-applicable",
      "rationale": "Test samples factor is not applicable to this COU. The FDA GCBP experimental dataset uses a standardised bovine blood analog (ASTM F1841) rather than patient-derived samples; sample-to-sample variability is controlled by the standardised protocol and is not a credibility driver for this assessment."
    },
